7. Concluding Statement

Employment in this domain is not contingent upon solving the problem in question. Instead, it relies on maintaining productive engagement with an unresolved phenomenon, cultivating rigorous discourse in the absence of closure, and ensuring the continued viability of inquiry itself.

Accordingly, the absence of evidence is not a barrier to entry; it is the operational premise of the field.
